7600031


	1. Set device security, i.e. pattern, PIN or password.
2. Add fingerprints
3. Pair device with bluetooth companion device (i. e. Smart watch or fitness wristband) which support Smart Lock function. In my test case it was MiBand 3 and Alcatel onetouch Go Watch.
4. Set Smart Lock settings to allow trusted BT device unlock UE when trusted device is nearby.
5. Use device for some time.